&sk RIGHT_ALT      &kp HRM_PINKY      &kp HRM_RING       &kp HRM_MIDDLE     &kp HRM_INDEX      &none   &kp HOME  &kp LEFT     &kp DOWN   &kp RIGHT      &kp END          &kp INSERT
